-- Etiqa Takaful issues 300 mln ringgit sukuk
-- 
-- Fri May 30, 2014 10:45PM EDT
-- None



KUALA LUMPUR, May 31 (Reuters) - Etiqa Takaful Bhd, Malaysia's largest takaful (Islamic insurance) operator and a unit of Maybank <MBBM.KL>, has raised 300 million Malaysian ringgit ($93.37 million) with an Islamic bond, the first from an Islamic insurer.

Proceeds from the 10-year sukuk will go toward funding general business operations and working capital, Etiqa Takaful said in a filing to the central bank on Friday. Maybank Investment Bank advised the deal.